17;ve appreciated very much has been the young Tenor RUBENS PELIZZARI , a gorgeous CANIO , a strong , beautyfull Voice and a dramtatic Actor ! It wa many years I was wayting for a new Canio and finally PELIZZARI is arrived . I know he&#8217;s going to sing TURANDOT , under the baguette of Zubin METHA .<br /> I hope someone can record his Performance as CALAF : I bet he will be GREAT ! All the best to GB OPERA and congratulation for your wonderfull work !!! TOM .</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-15401"> <article id="comment-15401" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c6b03c164d49d16444f53ceb3e89ff6f?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Tom</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/02/verona-teatro-filarmonicopagliacci/#comment-15401"><time datetime="2012-07-23T16:12:16+00:00">23 luglio 2012 at 16:12</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>It&#8217;s me again , Tom .<br /> I apologize for my mistake !<br /> I wanted to write that Franco ZEFFIRELLI (not Zezzirelli)  was great : his PAGLIACCI are always a big surprise &#8211; he always delivers !!</p><p>See you soon on GB OPERA .<br /> TOM .</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2012/02/verona-teatro-filarmonicopagliacci/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span 